What do i have?  
A comparison of the reduced chisq values for an exponential decay model of muon decay data. This is an interactive plot that i don't know how to embed in markdown. It is available at:
`[Histgram Reduced ChiSq v nBins](https://www.ianhi.github.io/ChiSqPlot.html)`
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
